{"tid":646890,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的，我個fd寫咗個M記掃code app","createTime":"2018-04-29T12:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T05:04:55.000Z","uid":29308,"like":28,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0aed300c79b02f56b30a6405e241a75709903a7d","tid":646890,"uid":29308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟個fd寫咗個M記掃code app（有埋網頁版），雖然知道有人做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<a href=\"https://workdev.xyz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworkdev.xyz%2F&d=MfFOQdkPCtCIbPE6r2e4gS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=663ac3d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://workdev.xyz/</a><br />\n等大家上網落完單之後可以即刻報到，去到M記就拎得餐，唔使去到先等佢整，方便快捷。<br />\n大家有Apple Watch就可以用Apple Watch開個code出嚟scan，或者上網頁版scan咗先出門口，再或者要用兩部smart Device<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qem5ukg7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqem5ukg7&h=0608104b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家都可以幫手掃code upload令個code庫更完整<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gctma0v6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgctma0v6&h=db11eb63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家可以save底啲常去M記，咁就唔使下下去線上圖庫搵code<br />\n個舉報可以隱藏咗啲code<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cbwlvoiu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcbwlvoiu&h=459d2066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wda4hfrs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwda4hfrs&h=2d007bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以del返唔要啲code<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/34nb28cu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F34nb28cu&h=77bf9cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家有咩意見可以提出，個app會持續開發，遲下可能會加入其他功能，例如其他店要用到有關QR code嘅野都可能加入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/scp1509j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fscp1509j&h=16b95989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有興趣掃code下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8239394cdb0a6eb048cbd3776334b8d0ed2477","tid":646890,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"落廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001bebf24e565ee08264c67e0e26158347721323","tid":646890,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"門檻都達唔到 冇兩部機呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d65036a1487128c8a0023a422a7be02c7e63c9d","tid":646890,"uid":29308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"001bebf24e565ee08264c67e0e26158347721323","tid":646890,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"門檻都達唔到 冇兩部機呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"SCAN完先落去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd23d864805299b9afce5675a6da3b8ede47ba3","tid":646890,"uid":64601,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"ad8239394cdb0a6eb048cbd3776334b8d0ed2477","tid":646890,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"落廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"咁細有咩問題，免費幫你做好冇？"},{"pid":"15775eaf6294d7b6fd9c31f47814ff5ba01bc78a","tid":646890,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"6bd23d864805299b9afce5675a6da3b8ede47ba3","tid":646890,"uid":64601,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"ad8239394cdb0a6eb048cbd3776334b8d0ed2477","tid":646890,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"落廣告 <img src=\"/assets/